[gd_resource type="Theme" load_steps=8 format=3 uid="uid://b3degg0toontheme"]

; Shared toon UI theme (M16, Chunk 81). One warm cream-on-dark palette with rounded panels +
; chunky cartoon buttons, applied to LevelSelect / Hud / ResultMenu / PauseMenu / CardBrawl so the
; whole front-end matches the in-game cel look. Buttons get filled rounded styleboxes (normal / hover
; / pressed / disabled / focus); Labels + Panels get the shared cream/dark defaults.

